## Hyprlua-lol


My Hyprland dotfiles for Arch GNU/Linux 


## What's included

* `foot/` (foot config)
* `wofi/` (wofi config)
* `hypr/` (hyprland config + other goodies)
* `waybar/` (waybar config)

## Goodies

* `hypr/walls/*` (wallpapers)


## Deps

* wofi
* foot
* hyprland
* swaybg
* swayosd
* neovim
* GoMono Nerd Font
* Waybar

## Install

```sh
git clone https://github.com/kantiankant/Hyprlua-lol && cd Hyprlua-lol && rm README && cp -r * ~/.config && cd ~/
```

## Basic Binds and such


* super + q: open foot
* super + w: close 
* super + shift + e: close hyprland
* super + hjkl: swap focus to respective direction
* super + shift + hjkl: swap window with any available window in the respective direction
* super + space: wofi --show drun

